{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1269/comments/3719106.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:4abf7fe95ae4..7d2654784d9e?path=gazebo%2Fgui%2FMainWindow.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1269/_/diff#comment-3719106"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1269, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1269.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1269"}}, "title": "Hide left GUI event"}, "content": {"raw": "How about something like this? It avoids forcibly closing the right pane.\n\n\n```\n#!c++\n\nint leftPane = _on ? MINIMUM_TAB_WIDTH : 0;\nint rightPane = this->splitter->sizes().at(2);\n\nQList<int> sizes;\nsizes.push_back(leftPane);\nsizes.push_back(this->width() - leftPane - rightPane);\nsizes.push_back(rightPane);\n\nthis->splitter->setSizes(sizes);\n```\n\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>How about something like this? It avoids forcibly closing the right pane.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-c++\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">leftPane</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">_on</span> <span class=\"o\">?</span> <span class=\"nl\">MINIMUM_TAB_WIDTH</span> <span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">rightPane</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"k\">this</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">splitter</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">sizes</span><span class=\"p\">().</span><span class=\"n\">at</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">QList</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"kt\">int</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">sizes</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"n\">sizes</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">push_back</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">leftPane</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"n\">sizes</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">push_back</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">this</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">width</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">leftPane</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">rightPane</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"n\">sizes</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">push_back</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">rightPane</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">this</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">splitter</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">setSizes</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">sizes</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-11-04T03:54:25.791312+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "inline": {"to": 1720, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "gazebo/gui/MainWindow.cc"}, "updated_on": "2014-11-04T03:54:25.798209+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 3719106}